$interpreted: Uzziah: You just don't give up, do you?

Naya: Identify yourself! All this unrest in the prairie...
The creatures...I know you're responsible!
Uzziah: They...
Uzziah: The effects were...unexpected.
Naya: WHO YOU ARE! Tell me now or this gets ugly.
Uzziah: The sorcerer from Atlas...trouble follows you like a stench.
Tica: Trouble? But, I'm a good girl~
Naya: Enough. We'll interrogate him!
Pang: Are you injured?
Naya: D-Damn, how did he...
Uzziah: ...Our confidence was misplaced, it seems.
Naya: It's not over. I'm not done with you yet!
Uzziah: Give up.
Uzziah: Everything's falling into place. The time has come for me to take my leave.
Naya: STAY RIGHT THERE!
Naya: I can't take this! I JUST CAN'T TAKE THIS! Who does this guy think he is......
Pang: Can he really control monsters?
Tica: Seems like it. He's tamed them somehow...
Tica: I'd better tell Headmaster Ceres when I get back!

Naya: I'll notify my superiors about this as well. 
Next time I see that scoundrel, he'll be in for a proper beating!
Tica: Is it that late already?
Tica: It's sad to see you all go, but I still must announce that Team Tica is dismissed!
Tica: Thank you so much, I love you all! Thank you teammates for all your hard work!
Naya: Let's make this crystal clear. I am not YOUR teammate!
Naya: But I will say, your arcane magic...couldn't have gotten here without it!
Pang: As my partner is nowhere to be seen, I must continue on my path.
Tica: Then let's leave it up to fate to bring Team Tica together again!
Pang: Until next time.
Naya: Farewell, my new friend!
Pang: Did you say... friend? I'd best find Puggi fast.
Pang: Formidable foe, I shall one day become your equal...
